textContent:
Boundaries are about what I need to feel self love, and self respect 

Boundaries are going to also be what gil needs to feel self love and self respect as my partner 

And this needs to be accepted as part of path 1. 

Boundaries are about clarifying when we cannot bring our full focus and attention and when and where we can
